OVERVIEW
Support a new era of R&D with enterprise agentic AI
Microsoft Discovery app (preview)
Get started with Microsoft Discovery with a localized experience that works using GitHub Copilot and your own working environment. Download the Microsoft Discovery app (preview) to start exploring today.
Agentic Discovery engine
Enable people and specialized agents to reason, plan, execute, and learn together on a continuous cycle with the Microsoft Discovery engine, a multi-agent tool that mirrors the scientific method.
Comprehensive R&D platform and ecosystem
Enable the full research and development lifecycle, from idea generation through experiemnt execution, results analysis, and continuous iteration. Bring your preferred models, tools, and data into an open, extensible platform designed to support your research workflows.
Enterprise-grade trust and security
Meet enterprise expectations from the start with a platform built on Azure and developed using Microsoft’s security development lifecycle, with security, compliance, transparency, and human oversight embedded throughout discovery.
